===Proper noun===
'''Batman''' (''strictly'' '''the Batman'''; ''originally'' '''the Bat-Man''')

#A [[fictional]] [[superhero]] in [[comic strip]]s (and later [[animated]] [[cartoon]]s and [[film]]s) who fights [[crime]] in Gotham City using a [[Bat]] motif with the assistance of his [[sidekick]] [[Robin]].
